# Hospital Core — Unified UI/UX Implementation Plan

Implement the entire frontend UI/UX to match the `design-system.md` specification, ensuring visual consistency across all ~60 screens (Admin, Staff, Portal, Public).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Breaking visual change:** Every page in the system will look different after this work. The old mixed shell designs are replaced by a **single unified layout** per module type.

> [!WARNING]
> **Font change:** The current `Public Sans` font is replaced by `Inter` as the primary sans-serif.

---

## Current State — Visual Audit (from screenshots)

The screenshots reveal **four distinct, inconsistent shell designs** across the application. This is the core problem being solved.

### Shell Design 1: Staff Layout (closest to design system ✅)
Dark navy topbar with tabs, light sidebar with workspace card, white content area.

![Staff Dashboard — current state](C:/Users/NITRO/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8c926624-a93c-4aeb-b15e-cc7da1730de0/screenshots/staff_dashboard.png)

**What's right:** Topbar color, sidebar workspace card, KPI cards, page title hierarchy.
**What's wrong:** Topbar shows "HOSPITAL CORE" differently per page; some pages show active blue bar under tab, some don't; sidebar width/icons vary.

### Shell Design 2: Admin Layout ("MEDCORE PORTAL" ❌)
Dark navy **left sidebar** with "MEDCORE PORTAL" branding, uppercase nav labels, `+ NEW ENTRY` CTA, no topbar tabs.

![Admin News — current state with wrong shell](C:/Users/NITRO/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8c926624-a93c-4aeb-b15e-cc7da1730de0/screenshots/admin_news.png)

**Problems:** Completely different shell from Staff. Brand says "MEDCORE PORTAL" instead of "HOSPITAL CORE". Dark sidebar violates the design system (should be light `#FBFCFE`). No topbar. Uppercase nav labels.

### Shell Design 3: Doctor/Finance Layout (hybrid ❌)
Dark blue left sidebar, minimal topbar with "Dashboard / Finance" tabs only, different brand icon.

![Doctor Dashboard — hybrid layout](C:/Users/NITRO/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8c926624-a93c-4aeb-b15e-cc7da1730de0/screenshots/doctor_dashboard.png)

![Finance Invoices — hybrid layout](C:/Users/NITRO/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8c926624-a93c-4aeb-b15e-cc7da1730de0/screenshots/finance_invoices.png)

**Problems:** Dark sidebar (should be light). "HOSPITAL CORE Management System" instead of just "HOSPITAL CORE". Top nav only has 2 tabs. User avatar is just a circle icon, not initials-based.

### Shell Design 4: Portal Layout ("MediCore" ❌)
Dark navy left sidebar with "MediCore HOSPITAL CORE" branding, green status dot on user avatar.

![Portal Assigned Staff — wrong shell](C:/Users/NITRO/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8c926624-a93c-4aeb-b15e-cc7da1730de0/screenshots/portal_assigned_staff.png)

**Problems:** Brand says "MediCore" not "HOSPITAL CORE". Dark sidebar. Different CTA style ("+ Book Appointment"). Different user profile layout.

### Public Pages (mixed quality)
Public pages have the most consistency — dark navy topbar with "HOSPITAL CORE", navigation links, and white content area.

![Public Home — reference](C:/Users/NITRO/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8c926624-a93c-4aeb-b15e-cc7da1730de0/screenshots/public_home.png)

![Public Doctors — reference](C:/Users/NITRO/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8c926624-a93c-4aeb-b15e-cc7da1730de0/screenshots/public_doctors.png)

