## Consistency Issues Summary

````carousel
### Issue 1: Four different brand names
- "HOSPITAL CORE" (Staff)
- "MEDCORE PORTAL" (Admin)
- "HOSPITAL CORE Management System" (Doctor/Finance)
- "MediCore HOSPITAL CORE" (Portal)

**Fix:** All should say **HOSPITAL CORE** with shield/cross icon.
<!-- slide -->
### Issue 2: Mixed sidebar styles
- Light `#FBFCFE` sidebar (Staff) ← Correct per design system
- Dark navy sidebar (Admin, Doctor, Finance, Portal) ← Wrong

**Fix:** All authenticated layouts use light sidebar.
<!-- slide -->
### Issue 3: Inconsistent topbar
- Full nav tabs: Dashboard, Patients, Queue, Inventory, Finance (Staff)
- Only 2 tabs: Dashboard, Finance (Doctor/Finance)
- No topbar at all (Admin, Portal — sidebar-only navigation)

**Fix:** All use the same topbar with role-appropriate tabs.
<!-- slide -->
### Issue 4: Footer inconsistency
- Some pages show footer, some don't
- Footer uses `#161616` (old carbon black), not `#061735` (navy)

**Fix:** Standardize footer or remove from authenticated pages.
````

---

## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 1. **Landing page:** The public home page uses a custom dark hero design. Should it remain untouched, or align to `--hc-*` navy tokens?
> 2. **Footer:** Should `<HmsFooter />` be removed from authenticated pages (not shown in design system)?
> 3. **Responsive sidebar collapse:** Implement the 84px tablet sidebar now, or defer?

---

## Target State — Design System Standard

Based on `design-system.md`, ALL authenticated pages must have:

| Element | Specification |
|---------|--------------|
| **Topbar** | 64px height, `#061735` (navy), shield+cross icon, "HOSPITAL CORE" brand, nav tabs, notifications, avatar |
| **Sidebar** | 280px width, `#FBFCFE` (light), workspace card, blue CTA, nav items with icons, system status card |
| **Content** | White background, 28px page title, 14px description, KPI grid, data panels with filter row |
| **Font** | Inter (primary), IBM Plex Mono (mono) |
| **Buttons** | 40px height, `#0F62FE` primary, rounded `10px` |
| **Badges** | Pill-shaped, semantic colors, 10-11px uppercase |
| **Cards** | `#E2E8F0` border, `14px` radius, `shadow-card`, hover lift |

---

## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Design Token Foundation ✅ DONE

- ✅ Rewrote `globals.css` with all `--hc-*` tokens
- ✅ Updated root layout font from Public Sans → Inter
- ✅ Added spacing, shadow, radius, motion tokens
- ✅ Updated shadcn semantic mappings

---

### Phase 2: App Shell Components

Unify all four shell designs into a single parametric shell.

#### [MODIFY] [top-nav.tsx](file:///d:/projects/hospital-management-system/web/src/components/shells/top-nav.tsx)

**Current → Target transformation:**

![Staff Dashboard — current topbar reference](C:/Users/NITRO/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8c926624-a93c-4aeb-b15e-cc7da1730de0/screenshots/staff_dashboard.png)

The Staff Dashboard topbar (above) is closest to the target. Changes needed:
- Height: ensure exactly `64px` via `var(--hc-topbar-h)`
- Background: `var(--hc-navy-950)` (`#061735`)
- Brand: Shield/cross icon + "HOSPITAL CORE" text, 18px/700
- Nav tabs: Active tab gets 3px bottom blue bar (`::after` pseudo)
- Grid: `280px minmax(0,1fr) auto` columns
- Actions: Bell with red notification dot, settings gear, avatar with initials + name + role

#### [MODIFY] [side-nav.tsx](file:///d:/projects/hospital-management-system/web/src/components/shells/side-nav.tsx)

**Current dark sidebar → Target light sidebar:**

The admin "MEDCORE PORTAL" dark sidebar and portal "MediCore" dark sidebar must both become:
- Width: `280px`
- Background: `var(--hc-sidebar-bg)` (`#FBFCFE`)
- Workspace card: 54×54px icon tile, title "Clinical Suite", subtitle "STANDARD ACCESS"
- CTA: Full-width blue button with shadow
- Nav items: 48px height, Lucide icons (20px), active = blue-50 bg + blue text + 4px left bar
- Bottom: Support, Logout, System Status card

#### [MODIFY] Module Layouts

All three layout files need to use the shared shell:

| Layout file | Current shell | Target |
|------------|--------------|--------|
| [admin/(app)/layout.tsx](file:///d:/projects/hospital-management-system/web/src/app/admin/(app)/layout.tsx) | Inline dark sidebar ("MEDCORE PORTAL") | `<HcTopbar>` + `<HcSidebar>` with admin links |
| [staff/(app)/layout.tsx](file:///d:/projects/hospital-management-system/web/src/app/staff/(app)/layout.tsx) | `<StaffTopNav>` + `<StaffSideNav>` | `<HcTopbar>` + `<HcSidebar>` with staff links |
| [portal/(app)/layout.tsx](file:///d:/projects/hospital-management-system/web/src/app/portal/(app)/layout.tsx) | Dark sidebar ("MediCore") | `<HcTopbar>` + `<HcSidebar>` with portal links |

