### Phase 3: Base UI Components

#### [MODIFY] [button.tsx](file:///d:/projects/hospital-management-system/web/src/components/ui/button.tsx)
- Primary: `#0F62FE`, hover `#0B4EDB`, blue shadow, 40px height, 13px/700
- Secondary: white bg, `#E2E8F0` border, 40px height
- Add `filter` variant

#### [MODIFY] [badge.tsx](file:///d:/projects/hospital-management-system/web/src/components/ui/badge.tsx)

Current badges use inconsistent styles. The screenshots show good semantic badges that need to be standardized:
- `success`: green text `#079669` on `#DDFBEA` (e.g., "ACTIVE", "Ready", "PAID")
- `warning`: orange text `#EA580C` on `#FFEDD5` (e.g., "PENDING", "UNPAID")
- `danger`: red text `#DC2626` on `#FEE2E2` (e.g., "CRITICAL", "URGENT")
- `info`: blue text `#2563EB` on `#DBEAFE` (e.g., "ACTIVE SESSION")
- `purple`: purple text `#7C3AED` on `#F3E8FF` (e.g., "EXPIRING SOON")

#### [NEW] [kpi-card.tsx](file:///d:/projects/hospital-management-system/web/src/components/ui/kpi-card.tsx)

The KPI cards in the staff dashboard screenshot show the correct pattern:

![Staff Dashboard KPI cards](C:/Users/NITRO/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8c926624-a93c-4aeb-b15e-cc7da1730de0/screenshots/staff_dashboard.png)

- 60×60px colored icon tile (blue, green, amber, red variants)
- Uppercase label (12px/800)
- Large value (30px/700)
- Helper text (12px/500)
- Card border + shadow + hover lift

#### [NEW] [data-panel.tsx](file:///d:/projects/hospital-management-system/web/src/components/ui/data-panel.tsx)
- Container card wrapping search/filter row + table
- Filter row: search input + dropdown filters + action buttons

#### [NEW] [page-header.tsx](file:///d:/projects/hospital-management-system/web/src/components/ui/page-header.tsx)
- 28px/700 title, 14px/400 description, optional action button

