## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. `npm run build` must pass after each phase
2. Run Playwright test suite for functional regressions

### Visual Checkpoints

| Checkpoint | Pass Criteria |
|-----------|--------------|
| Topbar | 64px, `#061735`, "HOSPITAL CORE" brand, nav tabs |
| Sidebar | 280px, `#FBFCFE`, workspace card, blue CTA |
| Active nav | Blue-50 bg + blue text + 4px left bar |
| Brand consistency | "HOSPITAL CORE" everywhere (no "MEDCORE", "MediCore") |
| Primary buttons | `#0F62FE` with blue shadow |
| Status badges | Correct semantic colors |
| KPI cards | 112px+, icon tile, uppercase label |
| Table headers | Uppercase, 11px, muted color |
| Border radius | 10–14px on cards (not 0px) |
| Font | Inter family on all text |
